sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Campuses Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open campuses page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query campuses with linked institutes
    DB-->>LW: Campus collection
    LW-->>UI: Render table and form modal state

    User->>UI: Search/filter/reset
    UI->>LW: Update filter properties / clear()
    LW->>DB: Re-query campuses
    DB-->>LW: Filtered campuses
    LW-->>UI: Re-render table

    User->>UI: Create/update/delete campus
    UI->>LW: save() / deleteCampus(id)
    LW->>DB: Insert/update/delete campus and relations
    DB-->>LW: Persist result
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh list
